You can't just enter without permission, you
know...

This school uniform... it doesn't quite fit me
right... I wonder if it's revealing too much...

Hmm... It suits me quite well, doesn't it?  I'm
like the epitome of a vibrant female student in
her prime.
You definitely don't think that, right...?
But, are you really okay with it...?

Don't worry, the spell is firmly in place.
Everyone around will only see me as a well-endowed
female student.

Well... It's good to enjoy school, but this is a
place where many young people gather.

In that case... one's desires must also be
overflowing with youthful passion...

Huh...? (I wonder if they agreed to help because
of that...)

Well then, it's been a while since I've had some
school sexual activities... I'll enjoy myself to
the fullest

Even though I have a school uniform, if a middle-
aged woman like me wears it, it will be obvious
right away...

I wonder if Rei-san's psychic powers can somehow
help with this?

In order to enter the school, you need to progress
through events with Rei.

Rei-san taught me psychic powers, but the crucial
thing is that I don't have any clothes to wear...

I wonder if they have it in the shopping district
or something...?

To enter the school, you need to obtain a school
uniform. Please progress through the event at the
general store in the shopping district.

School, huh... I used to wear a school uniform and
attend too... It brings back memories.

Hehe... It's fun as it is now, but I'd like to
experience the feeling of being a student again.

Hmm... Even if it's now, if you wear a school
uniform and enter, you can experience the feeling
of being a student.

W-What are you saying!? That's obviously not
allowed!

For someone like me, an older woman, to wear a
school uniform and go to school... unless it's
some kind of magic...

With my psychic powers, it's possible. I can use a
hypnotic illusion to make it work.

However, there are limits to hypnosis. If you wear
casual clothes, it might feel strange and the
hypnosis may not work.

At the very least, we need to acquire a school
uniform. And on top of that, you must learn the
magic. As for the magic... let's discuss it at my
place...

To enter school, you need to acquire a school
uniform and learn specific skills.

You can acquire a school uniform at the general
store in the shopping district, and you can learn
the skills from Rei at your home.

home!!

After the event ends, if you press the Q key, you
can hear Ayako's soliloquy about that event.

Basically, it doesn't affect the game progress if
you don't listen to it, but she might whisper
something that could lead to hints for capturing.

Also, be aware that if you fall asleep at home or
listen to the event-related soliloquy
once,\c[2]she won't whisper it again.\c[0] So
please be careful if you want to hear all the
conversations.
